name: FU
description: Fu is luck, a wild, wild ride. In your wallet, it’s all on your side! No Fu? Oh no! Life’s out of luck. Without it, you’re truly stuck! Dream of magic in your crypto tale? Fu the coin that turns fortune’s sail. Named for “luck” it’s here to ignite, bringing fortune to your wallet’s night. Fu’s not just another coin in the sea, It’s the spark of joy in your crypto spree. Join the Fu journey, where luck’s yours to hold, And turn your wallet’s story into gold!
